LSB License — Open Data Bundle
===============================

The LSB open data bundle is dedicated to the public domain under the Creative
Commons CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication. This covers
data/open_bundle/ and the Backblaze B2 / Zenodo distribution per
ARCHITECTURE.md §6.7.

The open data bundle contains: informants.jsonl (canonical raw data),
lsb.sqlite (query-friendly database), build_db.py (the build script),
DATA_DICTIONARY.md, and the v1 prompt templates. CC0 removes the attribution
requirement entirely and makes downstream reuse maximally frictionless.
Attribution is still strongly encouraged via the Zenodo DOI for citation
purposes, but not legally required.

See ARCHITECTURE.md §6.6 and §6.7 for the full rationale.

